<p>Melaka is a weekend destination, making us prime targets for "Staycations" that are actually disguised parties. We send a "Pre-Stay Questionnaire" to every local weekend booking. If they ask about parking capacity for multiple cars or if there are "cameras in the hallway," our screening goes into overdrive.</p>

<h2>3. The "Communication Velocity" Test</h2>
<p>How a guest behaves *before* they book is a perfect predictor of how they will behave *during* their stay. Demanding guests who ask for 50% discounts or 10 AM check-ins are statistically the most likely to leave a 1-star review. We respond to inquiries within 5-15 minutes to set a professional tone immediately.</p>

<h2>4. Verification Beyond the App</h2>
<p>Airbnb’s "Government ID Verified" badge is just the start. At iHousing, we go further with professional background checks and maintaining an "Internal Blacklist" across our 100+ managed properties in Melaka. If a guest caused trouble at one unit, they won't be getting into another.</p>

